# Project: ADM S&OP Dashboard
## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 (App Router)
- TypeScript (strict mode)
- Tailwind CSS v3
- shadcn/ui for all UI primitives
- Recharts for data visualization
- Supabase (client SDK + server actions)
- Zustand for global state management
- TanStack Query for server state
- Zod for validation

## Design System
- Font: Lora (headings), Inter (body/data)
- Primary color: Dark Blue (#1a2b4a) — EXL Partners brand
- Background: White (#ffffff)
- Positive: green-500, Negative: red-500, Neutral: slate-400
- All tables must support sorting, filtering, CSV export
- All charts must use Recharts with consistent color palette
- Mobile-first responsive design

## Code Style
- Functional components only, no classes
- Named exports (never default exports for components)
- Use 'use client' only when strictly necessary
- Prefer Server Components + Server Actions
- Descriptive variables: isLoading, hasError, forecastData
- File structure: components/, lib/, app/, types/

## Dashboard-Specific Rules
- KPI cards always at top of page
- Tables must support sorting, filtering, pagination
- All monetary values in GBP (£) by default
- Date format: DD MMM YYYY (UK format)
- Charts must have tooltips, legends, responsive containers
- Every table must have CSV export functionality
- Never use inline styles — Tailwind only
